data.description: Investment Property. Single level floor plan. Home being sold as is.  2 Bedrooms, 2 bath home with Living room, dining room, eat in kitchen and enclose porch area. Home was once a 3 bedroom. Buyer to connect water and electricity during due diligence period. Corner lot with carport. Bring all offers.
